text: Telemundo was a Italian pay television owned by NBCUniversal International Networks. The channel was available on Sky Italia. The channel launched on 14 October 2007. An HD feed was launched on 3 December 2007. The channel aired shows from the US Telemundo dubbed in Italian. The HD feed was replaced by NBC HD on 23 November 2010. However, the channel continues to operate on an SD feed until it closed on 24 November 2012 with content moving to NBC, which later closed on 24 November 2023.
